@startuml

/'
Activity Diagram – Basic Flow

Purpose:
Illustrates the fundamental flow of a process using start/stop points,
actions, and a simple decision.

*Elements:
- start/stop: Beginning and end of the flow
- :Action;: A single step in the process
- if/then/else: Conditional branching
'/

start
:Enter Username;
:Enter Password;
if (Credentials Valid?) then (yes)
  :Login Successful;
  stop
else (no)
  :Show Error Message;
  stop
endif

@enduml
